To learn more about using Bookshare with your device, visit the "Using Bookshare" page in the Help Center. Here is an overview of the specialized formats that Bookshare offers its members with links that go to the Help Center for more information. Bookshare Web Reader - a customized reading tool for Bookshare members offering all the features of DAISY with a single click of the "Read Now" link. DAISY (Digital Accessible Information System) - a digital book file format. DAISY books from Bookshare are DAISY 3.0 text files that work with just about every type of access technology that reads text. Books that contain images will have the download option of ‘DAISY Text with Images’. BRF (Braille Refreshable Format) - digital Braille for use with refreshable Braille devices and Braille embossers.
